ErrorSolution <p>Error</p> <pre><code>[
    {
        "keyword": "required",
        "dataPath": ".configuration",
        "schemaPath": "#/properties/configuration/required",
        "params": {
        "missingProperty": "resources.image"
        },
        "message": "should have required property 'resources.image'"
    }
]
</code></pre> <p>Success</p> <ol> <li>Click on the outer part (if empty - anywhere in the middle section; if there is files oder commandline arguements - click right next to them) in the middle section to open the Configuration of the Template</li> <li>Enter your Docker-Image</li> </ol>

